data.body:
It would be hugely helpful if we could see the generated GLSL for diagnostic purposes.

Here is some context: I'm having trouble with this (reduced) code for a 2D fragment shader:

```
vec3 s = tex(TEXTURE, UV).rgb;
s = pow(s,  1.0);
COLOR = color(1.0,1.0,0,1.0);
```

If you comment out the 2nd line it works. Otherwise, you get nothing + a strange glitch that lasts for a moment.
